    "updated_at": "2015-03-06T22:58:30Z",
    "body": "I'm super surprise Tilde works at all on either operating system, it really shouldn't. Tilde is a bash completion. Use this instead:\n\n```\nvar home = process.env.HOME || process.env.USERPROFILE;\npath.join(home, 'Untitled.png');\n```\n"
